    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "嗯？喂，尤蒂尔。\\n城堡外好像有人在争执哦。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "骑士",
            "context": "等等！伊尔凡！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "骑士",
            "context": "拜托了，\\n暂时留在我们骑士团吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "我一开始就说了吧，骑士团长。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "如果没法支付我要求的报酬，\\n我会马上辞职。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "骑士",
            "context": "呜……是这样，没错……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "骑士",
            "context": "但你要是走了，\\n我们骑士团就撑不下去了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "那就去赚钱啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "只要能给我钱，\\n不管什么工作我都会完美地解决。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "喂！尤蒂尔王子\\n在这座城堡里吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我就是尤蒂尔。\\n刚才的骑士，你不理他没关系吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "那种穷人，无所谓。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "比起这个……我叫伊尔凡。\\n是个佣兵。你有兴趣雇佣我吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "佣兵吗……我确实想要\\n能战斗的人才，可是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "那正好！虽然这话不该自己说，\\n不过我很好用哦。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "只要给我钱，\\n不管对方阵势多大，\\n我都能一个人挡下。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "他没有在吹牛。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "说到佣兵伊尔凡，\\n可是出了名的本领高强。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这样啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你愿意成为我的伙伴，\\n对我是大有帮助，但是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "那就是愿意雇佣我吧！好！\\n我们马上来谈谈报酬。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不是，听我说。\\n关于报酬……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "你是阿尔贝里亚的王子大人吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "既然是王子大人的骑士团，\\n那一定很有钱吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "雇佣我是对的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "只要给我钱，\\n我就发誓绝对效忠你。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "给足报酬的话，不管什么工作我都会完成。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "在你这种有钱人手下，\\n我就是最好的……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不，抱歉……\\n其实，我们很拮据。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "咦？啊？你在说什么。\\n你可是王子大人啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯，是这样没错……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "但我跟哥哥姐姐不同，\\n没有自己的领地，\\n也没有那么富裕……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "这……这……这算什么！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "啊～这样吗！那就算了！\\n就当没这回事！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "我就回到前雇主那……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "呃……可恶！\\n刚才我已经辞职了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这、这还真是抱歉……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "所以说……\\n你不加入我们了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "那……不，等等。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "虽然现在囊中羞涩，但他是王子……\\n将来没准他能成为一国之君。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "好吧……我就加入你们。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "平常我绝对不做这种事，\\n不过就等你出人头地再付钱吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "可以吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "嗯。就算回前雇主那里，\\n那些家伙也没什么钱……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "不过，你要记住。\\n我绝对不做白工。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "报酬方面，你有多少就付多少。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "伊尔凡",
            "context": "因为我做多少工作，\\n全都取决于报酬金额。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}